      "default": "GRANULARITY_MINUTE",
      "description": "Granularity for time-series aggregation (bucket size).\n\n - GRANULARITY_MINUTE: 1 minute intervals.\n - GRANULARITY_MINUTE_5: 5 minute intervals.\n - GRANULARITY_MINUTE_15: 15 minute intervals.\n - GRANULARITY_MINUTE_30: 30 minute intervals.\n - GRANULARITY_HOUR: 1 hour intervals.\n - GRANULARITY_HOUR_6: 6 hour intervals.\n - GRANULARITY_HOUR_12: 12 hour intervals.\n - GRANULARITY_DAY: 1 day intervals.\n - GRANULARITY_WEEK: 1 week intervals.\n - GRANULARITY_MONTH: 1 month intervals."
